Firestarter/Sixshot/Ares/Double Punch/Manterror/Injector:





Firestarter sat in the throne of the bridge of the Ramora.  He opened up a 
comm. link to four of the Neo Decepticons.

"Shockwave and Unitron so until they get back from their diplomatic missions 
I am in command.  Ares, Double Punch, Manterror, and Injector, you four will 
take care of the mission that fool Hell Beast was given.  Ares is in charge."

A few acknowledgements were received by Firestarter and the four NeoCons were 
on their way.
